      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/inflation-outlook-ecb-plans-to-make-crucial-wage-indicator-public-regularly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行正计划定期公布内部薪酬指标，官员们在考虑何时降息时会使用这些指标来衡量通胀风险。]]></description>
